orderedMerchandiseTop5: select  koProxyShopTitle as name, count(*) as y from proxy.orderedMerchandise where status !='UNPAID' group by merchandiseId order by y desc limit 5;
refundedMerchandiseTop5: select * from ((select  koProxyShopTitle as name, count(*) as y from proxy.orderedMerchandise where status ='CANCELED' group by merchandiseId order by y desc) as refundedMerchandise) group by name order by y desc limit 5;
